		<h1>Tag <code>T6G</code>: Socio-technical</h1>
		Work foregrounding social, organisational, and human-system aspects intertwined with language engineering: socio-technical system modelling, governance and policy aspects encoded in languages, and human/organisational constraints treated as first-class concerns.
